              <section className="space-y-4">
                <h2 className="text-2xl font-semibold text-white tracking-tight">4. Cookies and Local Storage</h2>
                <p>
                  We primarily operate in a stateless nature. N-NEX does not require accounts or user authentication, therefore no persistent session cookies are created. Aside from standard diagnostic cookies potentially set by our infrastructure provider (Vercel), any ephemeral data produced by our AST generator uses your browser's RAM, and optionally the Clipboard API upon your explicit request.
                </p>
              </section>

              <section className="space-y-4">
